  "nodes": {
    "n25": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "—— 两 天 后 ——",
      "next": "n26"
    },
    "n26": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "大晴天。鸟叫。城外土路上，牛车碾过辙印。关二狗坐在路边石头上：头发乱成鸡窝，眼下两团青黑。他盯着地上一只蚂蚁，看了很久，很久。",
      "next": "n27"
    },
    "n27": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "player"
      },
      "text": "……好饿。",
      "next": "n28",
      "portrait": {
        "emotion": "empty_eyes"
      }
    },
    "n28": {
      "type": "line",
      "speaker": {
        "kind": "literal",
        "name": "旁白"
      },
      "text": "他站起来，拍拍屁股，往城里走。身上还是自己那身破衣裳——梦里的东西，一件都没跟出来。除了饿。",
      "next": "n_wake"
    },
    "n_wake": {
      "type": "runActions",
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "emitNarrativeSignal",
          "params": {
